  <brief_title>Invasive and Non-Invasive Assessment of Cerebral Oxygenation in Patients With Severe Traumatic Brain Injury (TBI)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Validation of Non- Invasive Regional Transcranial Oxygen Saturation (rSO2) by Comparison With Invasive Brain Tissue Oxygenation (PbtO 2) Measurement in Patients With Severe Traumatic Brain Injury</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
